{
  "stem": "27409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was part of the Ukraine now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Bucovina, but it's changed from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'46 I think, April.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's in the South was Bucovina, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there they lived by [INAUDIBLE] you know, as American [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a Jewish community from local, which had also returned from deportation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one helped the other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, my father died the day of his [INAUDIBLE], he died, the 24th 1946, December 1946.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother died a few months later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister was left alone from the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came on Alia in '50-- '50-- 1950.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She came to Italy to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't go because if you ask a Russian you want to go in this direction, he sends you in the opposite direction.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, they couldn't 't me-- not send me to Germany because they had-- the order was given, secret order-- I didn't know about it-- not to send Jews or westerners.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were considered westerner for the newly occupied territory '40, which were occupied from Poland or from Bucovina.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not to send Germany because they run over to-- to the capitalist world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was sent to Romania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the Romania, I was the Allied Commission.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First, I was searching for my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I found them in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- it was about a month too with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I used my-- you had to earn money because-- so I worked putting mines in a stone work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, I had to go back to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There I met to announce myself ready for duty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There with the Allied Commission there were friends of mine from school, which came back as officers in the Eighth Army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some of them, Fishman in particular, was my school friend, primary school.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
